No. 11-7457. Robert Smith, Petitioner v. United States. 565 U.S. 1148, 132 S. Ct. 1051,

181 L. Ed. 2d 792,

2012 U.S. LEXIS 504. January 9, 2012.

Petition for writ of certiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Seventh Circuit denied.
